Maintainer: fehlix <fehlix@mxlinux.org>
Changed-By: fehlix <fehlix@mxlinux.org>
Description:
 user-installed-packages - list user installed packages
Changes:
 user-installed-packages (26.05.1) mx; urgency=medium
 .
   * Check package cache before building the install list
     - warn and offer apt update if package cache is empty or outdated
     - show error dialog when apt update fails, with option to continue anyway
     - use own update stamp as fallback on systems without apt periodic stamp hook
     - add please-wait progress dialog during package availability checks
   * Remove redundant apt update from uip-apt-install (now handled by cache check)
   * Remove dependency of python3-pyqt6 and xdotool
   * Use yad to display "About" window
   * Add --version flag
   * Translations refresh
